00:26:13.280 --> 00:26:17.050
some special function
that has a parameter a,

00:26:17.050 --> 00:26:19.450
for which this
operator gives you

00:26:19.450 --> 00:26:21.870
a times that special function.

00:26:21.870 --> 00:26:24.670
And that special
