00:45:20.140 --> 00:45:24.070
is equal to i h bar
times the unit operator.

00:45:28.700 --> 00:45:30.790
Apart from the
Schrodinger equation,

00:45:30.790 --> 00:45:33.160
this is probably the
most important equation

00:45:33.160 --> 00:45:34.190
